<p>The <code>bool</code> tag stores a boolean value to the store.</p>

<h2>Basic Bool Usage</h2>
<pre>{open}bool 'hasItems'{close}
{open}if {open}get 'hasItems'{close} eq TRUE{close}Has items{open}else{close}No items{open}/if{close}</pre>
{bool 'hasItems'}
<p>Result: {if {get 'hasItems'} eq TRUE}Has items{else}No items{/if}</p>

<h2>Setting TRUE/FALSE</h2>
<pre>{open}set isEnabled=TRUE{close}
{open}set isDisabled=FALSE{close}
Enabled: {open}if $isEnabled eq TRUE{close}Yes{open}else{close}No{open}/if{close}
Disabled: {open}if $isDisabled eq TRUE{close}Yes{open}else{close}No{open}/if{close}</pre>
{set isEnabled=TRUE}
{set isDisabled=FALSE}
<p>Enabled: {if $isEnabled eq TRUE}Yes{else}No{/if}</p>
<p>Disabled: {if $isDisabled eq TRUE}Yes{else}No{/if}</p>

<h2>Boolean in Conditions</h2>
<pre>{open}set showDetails=TRUE{close}
{open}if $showDetails eq TRUE{close}
  &lt;div&gt;Here are the details...&lt;/div&gt;
{open}/if{close}</pre>
{set showDetails=TRUE}
{if $showDetails eq TRUE}
<div style="border:1px solid #ccc; padding:10px;">Here are the details...</div>
{/if}

<h2>Toggle Boolean</h2>
<pre>{open}set flag=TRUE{close}
Before: {open}if $flag eq TRUE{close}TRUE{open}else{close}FALSE{open}/if{close}
{open}set flag=FALSE{close}
After: {open}if $flag eq TRUE{close}TRUE{open}else{close}FALSE{open}/if{close}</pre>
{set flag=TRUE}
<p>Before: {if $flag eq TRUE}TRUE{else}FALSE{/if}</p>
{set flag=FALSE}
<p>After: {if $flag eq TRUE}TRUE{else}FALSE{/if}</p>
